1
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:57,501
How does it feel to be a demon?

2
00:01:00,941 --> 00:01:02,140
Your Highness,

3
00:01:02,420 --> 00:01:03,621
it's you!

4
00:01:03,621 --> 00:01:05,700
This is just a fraction of the suffering

5
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:07,300
you've imposed on the demon clan.

6
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:08,300
Can't handle it already?

7
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:10,741
I'll kill you one day.

8
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:20,780
With demon hunters surrounding you,

9
00:01:22,901 --> 00:01:24,220
you'd better not get captured

10
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:25,741
before you can kill me.

11
00:01:30,741 --> 00:01:31,500
What demon dares

12
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:32,860
to provoke in the Prince Xian's Mansion?

13
00:01:33,140 --> 00:01:33,780
Today,

14
00:01:34,101 --> 00:01:35,461
you won't get away!

15
00:01:40,060 --> 00:01:41,300
Demon's madness,

16
00:01:41,741 --> 00:01:43,021
Netherworld Soul Capture,

17
00:01:43,101 --> 00:01:44,420
Three Pure Bells ring,

18
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,700
surrender and be bound!

19
00:01:51,661 --> 00:01:53,220
I can make you a demon

20
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:55,420
and hide your aura.

21
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:57,300
But I have one condition:

22
00:01:57,621 --> 00:01:58,300
from now on,

23
00:01:58,940 --> 00:02:00,340
you must obey me.

24
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:02,461
I've spent my life fighting evil.

25
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:03,700
Even if I die,

26
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:06,621
I'll never submit to a demon like you!

27
00:02:16,941 --> 00:02:18,221
Your hands are stained

28
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:20,700
with innocent blood,

29
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,740
yet you still have the nerve to speak?

30
00:02:29,541 --> 00:02:31,020
Why can I heal myself?

31
00:02:34,061 --> 00:02:35,381
In this world, only I can

32
00:02:35,740 --> 00:02:37,180
truly kill you.

33
00:02:39,501 --> 00:02:40,501
Yet you

34
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:42,501
can't harm me.

35
00:02:44,180 --> 00:02:47,381
You must endure the pain of being a demon.

36
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:54,180
Listen,

37
00:02:55,501 --> 00:02:56,900
Even if I am a demon,

38
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:59,381
as long as I uphold justice,

39
00:02:59,981 --> 00:03:01,661
I can still protect the people!

40
00:03:01,661 --> 00:03:02,700
How ridiculous!

41
00:03:03,821 --> 00:03:05,781
You are an evil spirit plaguing the people,

42
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,541
yet you preach righteousness and virtue.

43
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:09,420
Claiming to fight evil,

44
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:10,941
yet you slaughter the innocent.

45
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:12,501
Tell me,

46
00:03:13,101 --> 00:03:14,661
if those demon hunters outside

47
00:03:14,661 --> 00:03:16,981
knew the so-called virtuous prince

48
00:03:16,981 --> 00:03:17,941
leading them is like this,

49
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:19,381
what would they do?

50
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:26,300
It was you

51
00:03:26,501 --> 00:03:28,101
who killed those innocent people!

52
00:03:28,341 --> 00:03:30,101
You must admit your mistakes!

53
00:03:31,541 --> 00:03:32,661
I didn't kill anyone!

54
00:03:34,501 --> 00:03:35,620
It wasn't me!

55
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:36,900
Does it matter who killed them?

56
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:37,821
You are a demon!

57
00:03:37,821 --> 00:03:39,860
In the eyes of the world, it's all your doing!

58
00:03:40,501 --> 00:03:41,460
I'm not a demon!

59
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:42,420
You are!

60
00:03:43,821 --> 00:03:44,661
Open your eyes

61
00:03:44,661 --> 00:03:45,541
and look at yourself!

62
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:46,541
If you're not a demon,

63
00:03:46,541 --> 00:03:47,661
why do you look like this?

64
00:03:47,941 --> 00:03:49,061
If you're not a demon,

65
00:03:49,061 --> 00:03:51,101
why doesn't the Soul-Devouring Bone Sword obey you?

66
00:04:03,341 --> 00:04:05,300
This is your reality now.

67
00:04:05,941 --> 00:04:07,661
You'll never be human again.

68
00:04:08,101 --> 00:04:09,221
You have no choice

69
00:04:09,781 --> 00:04:10,981
but to submit to me.

70
00:04:11,381 --> 00:04:12,221
Or,

71
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:14,261
I could let them in right now

72
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:15,781
and let them see

73
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:17,661
what their long-relied-upon

74
00:04:17,661 --> 00:04:18,820
Virtuous Prince truly looks like.

75
00:04:19,141 --> 00:04:19,701
Your Highness,

76
00:04:20,101 --> 00:04:21,380
the demon aura inside is thick.

77
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:23,420
I request permission to enter and slay it.

78
00:04:25,781 --> 00:04:27,740
I request permission to enter and slay it.

79
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,341
I promise you,

80
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:35,740
carry it with you,

81
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:37,620
and it will mask the demon aura.

82
00:04:59,260 --> 00:04:59,820
Your Highness,

83
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:00,981
where is the evil spirit?

84
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:05,781
It has been slain by me.

85
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:19,981
What?

86
00:05:20,341 --> 00:05:21,500
You don't believe me?

87
00:05:22,021 --> 00:05:22,500
I dare not.

88
00:05:22,981 --> 00:05:24,060
As long as Your Highness is safe.

89
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:25,221
I'll take my leave.

90
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:40,781
If you had been this obedient earlier,

91
00:05:41,300 --> 00:05:42,380
you wouldn't have suffered.

92
00:05:47,141 --> 00:05:48,500
What are you going to do now?

93
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,300
You'll know

94
00:05:50,021 --> 00:05:51,021
when night falls.

95
00:06:03,781 --> 00:06:04,581
No.

96
00:06:05,461 --> 00:06:06,380
It's not me.

97
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:15,981
Why bring me here?

98
00:06:16,701 --> 00:06:18,701
Qing Lan is utterly loyal to me.

99
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:19,500
No.

100
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,901
Don't you dare harm her!

101
00:06:20,901 --> 00:06:23,260
Can't you see she's tormented by nightmares?

102
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:26,221
No.

103
00:06:27,981 --> 00:06:29,101
Devour her nightmares,

104
00:06:29,701 --> 00:06:30,620
and you'll gain power.

105
00:06:32,661 --> 00:06:33,500
What if I refuse?

106
00:06:35,740 --> 00:06:37,300
Then the world will know

107
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,701
that the esteemed Prince Xian

108
00:06:39,021 --> 00:06:39,701
is nothing but a demon.

109
00:06:42,781 --> 00:06:43,581
No!

110
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:44,981
You're so despicable!

111
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:45,981
It's not me!

112
00:06:46,021 --> 00:06:47,981
Dream-Eating Demon survives on nightmares,

113
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,820
doesn't harm mortals,

114
00:06:50,221 --> 00:06:51,781
but helps them sleep better.

115
00:07:01,661 --> 00:07:02,581
What are you waiting for?

116
00:07:03,021 --> 00:07:04,180
If you delay me,

117
00:07:04,541 --> 00:07:05,461
I won't spare you!

118
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,380
Qing Lan,

119
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:18,940
I officially appoint you as the Commander.

120
00:07:18,981 --> 00:07:19,981
From now on,

121
00:07:20,021 --> 00:07:21,661
you must always be vigilant

122
00:07:21,781 --> 00:07:23,940
and be at my service at all times.

123
00:07:24,341 --> 00:07:25,740
I hope you will continue to

124
00:07:25,860 --> 00:07:26,820
live up to the heavy responsibility.

125
00:07:26,940 --> 00:07:28,420
I will fulfill my mission.

126
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:33,860
How can a woman in the army be more capable than us men?

127
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:35,740
But she has risen rapidly.

128
00:07:35,981 --> 00:07:37,620
It turns out that she used this method.

129
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:38,620
Of course.

130
00:07:38,740 --> 00:07:40,180
She pretends to be in love

131
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:42,141
to win the heart of His Highness the Virtuous King.

132
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:42,981
It's certainly easier

133
00:07:42,981 --> 00:07:45,620
to go through fire and water.

134
00:08:00,101 --> 00:08:00,701
This...

135
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:02,661
This is not me.

136
00:08:05,981 --> 00:08:07,661
Such behavior,

137
00:08:07,820 --> 00:08:09,500
thinking that by tearing the painting,

138
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:10,940
she could be safe.

139
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:12,341
This is not me.

140
00:08:12,581 --> 00:08:13,581
Just a woman.

141
00:08:14,701 --> 00:08:15,541
This is not me.

142
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:19,940
If not you, then who?

143
00:08:24,180 --> 00:08:24,940
Not me.

144
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:26,060
Not me.

145
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:44,061
Did you deliberately create this dream?

146
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:47,900
I'm not that despicable.

147
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:52,140
[Why does Qing Lan have such a portrait?]

148
00:08:52,341 --> 00:08:53,900
[There must be something fishy.]

149
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:58,260
[To fulfill the dreamer's desires]

150
00:08:58,421 --> 00:09:00,061
[is the way to devour nightmares.]

151
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:24,581
[So demons can cultivate]

152
00:09:24,701 --> 00:09:25,660
[without killing people.]

153
00:09:26,140 --> 00:09:27,380
Say it louder.

154
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:28,620
It's better to wake her up.

155
00:09:57,020 --> 00:10:00,101
[Why are there such patterns on the paper?]

156
00:10:03,061 --> 00:10:03,981
Your Highness, please forgive me.

157
00:10:03,981 --> 00:10:05,981
I've never done anything to tarnish my reputation,

158
00:10:05,981 --> 00:10:08,020
let alone the name of the mansion.

159
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:09,701
Please investigate clearly, Your Highness.

160
00:10:10,981 --> 00:10:11,701
Stand up.

161
00:10:15,341 --> 00:10:16,821
Were you forced to do this?

162
00:10:16,821 --> 00:10:17,421
No.

163
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:19,181
I've never done anything like this.

164
00:10:22,461 --> 00:10:24,500
It was Xiao Zimo, the shopkeeper of Chunbugui.

165
00:10:24,981 --> 00:10:25,701
He said

166
00:10:25,941 --> 00:10:27,581
he could paint portraits of women for free.

167
00:10:28,101 --> 00:10:29,101
I thought

168
00:10:29,341 --> 00:10:31,020
since I followed you to work,

169
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:32,221
since I followed you.

170
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:35,701
I thought I could give the portraits to my parents

171
00:10:36,020 --> 00:10:38,221
to show them what I look like as an official.

172
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:41,341
But he forged those portraits

173
00:10:41,421 --> 00:10:43,341
and forced me to redeem them at a high price.

174
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:46,660
You're skilled in martial arts.

175
00:10:46,941 --> 00:10:48,500
How could you be easily manipulated by him?

176
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:50,140
I also thought about not being threatened,

177
00:10:50,660 --> 00:10:52,181
and even thought about killing him.

178
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,540
But he said

179
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:55,260
he had already made a mold.

180
00:10:55,540 --> 00:10:56,421
Even if he died,

181
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:58,860
these paintings would still be spread.

182
00:11:01,301 --> 00:11:02,341
I'm incompetent,

183
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:03,701
but every word is true.

184
00:11:08,181 --> 00:11:10,260
I won't let you suffer unjustly.

185
00:11:10,941 --> 00:11:12,740
Anyone who dares to harm my people

186
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:13,860
will not be spared.

187
00:11:42,101 --> 00:11:45,020
[Xu Qinglai is Shen Daozhi's master.]

188
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:48,140
[Is he also connected to the Crimson Heart?]

189
00:11:54,181 --> 00:11:55,421
I'm Xiao Zimo.

190
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:56,341
Miss,

191
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:03,380
you're so beautiful.

192
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:05,260
Would you like to preserve

193
00:12:05,461 --> 00:12:06,301
your beauty?

194
00:12:10,701 --> 00:12:11,500
Please,

195
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,660
this is my work.

196
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:19,380
Nicely done.

197
00:12:19,701 --> 00:12:21,221
Would you do one for me too?

198
00:12:23,181 --> 00:12:23,740
Come,

199
00:12:24,181 --> 00:12:24,860
please.

200
00:12:42,260 --> 00:12:42,941
Sir,

201
00:12:43,421 --> 00:12:44,900
your seal's design

202
00:12:45,421 --> 00:12:46,581
is quite unique.

203
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:50,421
It's the legendary beast,

204
00:12:50,860 --> 00:12:51,900
known as Red Heart.

205
00:12:52,101 --> 00:12:53,701
It was wounded by a Great Demon

206
00:12:53,701 --> 00:12:54,860
while protecting the world.

207
00:12:54,981 --> 00:12:56,260
Its soul was shattered

208
00:12:56,380 --> 00:12:57,260
and scattered.

209
00:12:57,660 --> 00:12:58,540
Strange things

210
00:12:58,540 --> 00:13:00,181
happened in my shop.

211
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:02,421
Thanks to the State Preceptor Xu Qinglai,

212
00:13:02,981 --> 00:13:04,660
I began to worship this beast.

213
00:13:04,821 --> 00:13:05,821
Since then,

214
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,780
all has been peaceful.
